      "audio": "RR_003_s025.mp3",
      "playable": false,
      "seq": 25,
      "insight": null
    },
    {
      "type": "Dial",
      "speaker": "Mina",
      "emotion": "박수를 치며",
      "text": "제 말이요.",
      "translation": "My thoughts exactly.",
      "lang": "KO",
      "audio": "RR_003_s026.mp3",
      "playable": true,
      "seq": 26,
      "insight": null
    },
    {
      "type": "Dial",
      "speaker": "Mina",
      "emotion": "어이없어하며",
      "text": "카페에서 소리를 질러야 한다니까요.",
      "translation": "I'm saying we have to scream at the cafe.",
      "lang": "KO",
      "audio": "RR_003_s027.mp3",
      "playable": true,
      "seq": 27,
      "insight": null
    },
    {
      "type": "Dial",
      "speaker": "John",
      "emotion": "장난스럽게",
      "text": "Next time. Let's just go to a convenience store for coffee.",
      "translation": "",
      "lang": "EN",
      "audio": "RR_003_s028.mp3",
      "playable": false,
      "seq": 28,
      "insight": null
    },
    {
      "type": "Dial",
      "speaker": "Mina",
      "emotion": "웃으며",
      "text": "내 말이. 거기가 훨씬 편해요.",
      "translation": "My thoughts exactly. It's much more comfortable there.",
